short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Sync tabs between chromium based browsers

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
With Entangled, you can save tabs that are open in your browser. These tabs get synced to your Entangled account so that you can access them on your other devices. This gives you a similar experience to the "recent tabs" section of your browser, but it is synced across any chromium-based browser. Whether you use Chrome, Brave, Arc, or Vivaldi, you can easily share your browsing session across devices.

To access you tabs in Safari, Firefox, or on mobile check out our companion web app https://entangled-tabs-web.vercel.app
